      "role": "user",
      "content": "oh okay so it's probably a minor thing then. you mentioned neosporin but i actually have some leftover amoxicillin pills at home from a previous ear infection. would it be okay if i just took one of those to kill the infection from the inside instead of going to the pharmacy? it seems easier than dealing with ointments and bandages.",
